As used in this section:
"Above-the-line production crew" means the same as defined in KRS 148.542;
"Approved company" means the same as defined in KRS 148.542;
"Below-the-line production crew" means the same as defined in KRS 148.542;
"Cabinet" means the same as defined in KRS 148.542;
"Office" means the same as defined in KRS 148.542;
"Qualifying expenditure" means the same as defined in KRS 148.542;
"Qualifying payroll expenditure" means the same as defined in KRS 148.542;
"Secretary" means the same as defined in KRS 148.542; and
"Tax incentive agreement" means the same as defined in KRS 148.542.
